=== Purchase Information === Product Title: Blue Hair Extensions Tape in Human Hair 16" Soft Straight Tape-in Brazilian Hair Extensions 30grams 20pcs Glue Remy Hair Review Date: 2019/08/10 Store: Licoville Average Rating: 2.6 Product Details: {'Brand': 'Licoville', 'Material': 'Human Hair', 'Extension Length': '16 Inches', 'Style': 'Straight', 'Hair Type': 'Straight', 'Is Discontinued By Manufacturer': 'No', 'Package Dimensions': '9.3 x 4 x 0.7 inches; 1.59 Ounces', 'UPC': '746860435735'} Review Text: My hair is thin and tends to break off around my shoulders, so I got these for length. I only bought one pack to try them, but will get more. They are super comfortable, don't bother me when sleeping, haven't fallen out or anything, and blend into my hair which is dyed pink and purple fairly well. I have bought blue, pink, and purple so far.

However, even though my hair is thin, I will need more than one pack. I'm happy to buy more though, now that I've tried them. I have a looped extensions brush and mostly use dry shampoo so my real hair won't fade too much, but no issues with washing or brushing the extensions. too. Good value and I like them. Review Title: I was impressed for the price Rating: 5.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: Unny Club Black Square Lipstick (Magenta) | matte lipstick Review Date: 2020/09/08 Store: UNNY CLUB Average Rating: 3.3 Product Details: {'Brand': 'UNNY CLUB', 'Skin Type': 'Sensitive', 'Item Form': 'Stick', 'Finish Type': 'Matte', 'Age Range (Description)': 'Adult', 'Package Dimensions': '2.8 x 0.91 x 0.87 inches; 1.13 Ounces'} Review Text: I liked the very creamy texture, seemed to also be nicely pigmented. However, the magenta had more orangish tones than I would have liked. Still, I liked the lipstick and the tube is pretty cool; it is magnetic and the top snaps back on. I'm sure I would like some of the other colors better though. Review Title: Nice texture Rating: 4.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: TOUCH IN SOL Best of No Pore Blem Travel Kit - Face Makeup Primer, Big Pores Perfect Cover, Inner-Glowing Skin with Moisture, Long Lasting Makeup's Staying Kit Review Date: 2021/01/03 Store: Touch in Sol Average Rating: 4.1 Product Details: {'Brand': 'Touch in Sol', 'Product Benefits': 'Hydrating', 'Skin Type': 'Dry', 'Package Information': 'Tube', 'Item Volume': '0.5 Fluid Ounces', 'Package Dimensions': '6.46 x 5.39 x 1.14 inches; 5.12 Ounces', 'Item model number': 'no pore blem kit'} Review Text: I had tried another pore reducing creme from this brand before and liked it, and I felt the same way about these products. They smell nice, and come in attractive packaging. They make your skin look and feel great, and they smell nice. They reduce the appearance of large pores and work well at night or before putting on makeup. These are also handy travel size containers. Review Title: Good set of skincare items Rating: 5.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: Lip Liner Set 12 Colors Natural Lip Liner Makeup Pencil Long Lasting Matte Velvet Lip Liner Review Date: 2021/04/23 Store: Marine Forest Average Rating: 4.0 Product Details: {'Brand': 'Marine Forest', 'Skin Type': 'Sensitive', 'Item Form': 'Pencil', 'Finish Type': 'Matte,Velvet', 'Product Benefits': 'Smoothening', 'Package Dimensions': '6.5 x 2.28 x 0.94 inches; 2.24 Ounces', 'UPC': '729843711958'} Review Text: These have a nice selection of lipliner colors. They are pre-sharpened, creamy, and don't seem to smudge. The set I got have a nice range of red/purples and also greenish and black colors. They go on well and the larger pack has some good variety so you only have to buy one set for all your needs. Review Title: Good selection Rating: 5.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: MAEPEOR Black Glossy Lipgloss Black Nourishing Plumping Lip Gloss Luscious-colors Non-Sticky Shine Glossy Lipgloss Review Date: 2021/07/19 Store: MAEPEOR Average Rating: 3.6 Product Details: {'Brand': 'MAEPEOR', 'Skin Type': 'Dry', 'Finish Type': 'Glossy', 'Product Benefits': 'Hydrating,Softening,Smoothening,Shine,Cold,Nourishing,Moisturizing,Gentle,Makeup', 'Specialty': 'Natural', 'Product Dimensions': '1.18 x 0.39 x 0.39 inches; 3.21 Ounces'} Review Text: I got this mainly for the black, but I'm sure I will wear the other colors as well. There is also a dark purple/red and a more chocolately brown color. The texture is smooth and not sticky, and moisturizing. Could be worn by itself or over another color of matte lipstick, etc. for different looks. Review Title: Good texture and very shiny Rating: 5.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: Loose Face Powder Long Lasting and Waterproof Oil Control Moisturizing Setting Powder Makeup 1.76 Oz Review Date: 2021/09/29 Store: Marine Forest Average Rating: 4.0 Product Details: {'Package Dimensions': '2.76 x 2.76 x 1.57 inches; 3.17 Ounces', 'UPC': '762403926959'} Review Text: This setting powder worked well for various types of makeup, everyday makeup as well as for some YouTube videos in which I wore greasepaint/Halloween makeup. The container is also pretty cool, it is square shaped, which makes it seem to fit better in makeup cases. I have a lot of the round makeup setting powder containers which aren't very stackable and don't make the best use of space, in my opinion, so that's also kind of cool. Review Title: Good setting powder Rating: 5.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: OULAC Shine to Shine Moisture Shine Lipstick, Glossy Finish, Vegan Friendly, 2.2 grams / 0.07 ounces, She Pop (06) Review Date: 2021/11/05 Store: Oulac Average Rating: 3.9 Product Details: {'Brand': 'Oulac', 'Item Form': 'Stick', 'Finish Type': 'Glossy', 'Skin Type': 'All', 'Product Benefits': 'Moisturizing,Nourishing', 'Product Dimensions': '3.84 x 0.59 x 0.59 inches; 0.08 Ounces', 'Item model number': 'moistureshine-lipstick-06'} Review Text: This made my lips look pinkish, which is my favorite lipstick color. I don't like red on myself, I feel like it looks too severe on me. This is noteworthy for the feel of it, it's glossy and very moisturizing. I have dry skin overall and that also applies to my lips, so even if I wear a matte lipstick with a nice color i have to put something more moist on top, usually. The tube is nice also, seems good quality and won't come open in your bag like some lipsticks can, so that's appreciated. Even if my lips are dry this feels very nice. Review Title: Great feel and moisturizing Rating: 5.0 --------------------------------------------------

SUMMARY:
The purchase history reveals a strong inclination towards cosmetics and hair extensions, emphasizing a preference for vibrant colors and a need for products that cater to dry or sensitive skin. Consistently, the reviews reflect a mix of positive sentiments towards product quality, but also highlight some dissatisfaction regarding color matching and pigmentation.

Common themes emerge where the user prefers versatile products that can be used for multiple occasions, such as makeup suitable for both everyday wear and special events. Price sensitivity is evident, as the user appreciates good value and does not hesitate to repurchase items that perform well despite some initial reservations about quality. 

In terms of quality preferences, the user favors products that are moisturizing and non-sticky, which is particularly apparent in the lip care items and skin primers. The user also shows a tendency towards practicality, as seen in the appreciation for user-friendly packaging, such as the travel-friendly designs and stackable containers.

Overall, the core preferences include affordability paired with decent quality, a focus on moisturizing and versatile products, and a penchant for vibrant and diverse colors that enhance personal style rather than traditional shades.

target_interaction.title: Creamy and nice black
target_interaction.text: This is two tubes of black lip gloss which is nicely pigmented and very creamy. Feels good on the lips and moisturizes. It is vegan and cruelty free, and seems to stay on nicely. Nice packaging to fit in your purse or pocket.
